 VTuber Pekora Usada 第一次单独演唱会“Usagi the MEGAMI!!”将于 12 月 6 日在 Ariake Arena 举行https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-1st-solo-live-usagi-the-megami-will-be-held-on-december-6-at-ariake-arena/ https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-1st-solo-live-usagi-the-megami-will-be-held-on-december-6-at-ariake-arena/#respondp2y_admin Sat, 23 Sep 2023 12:57:33 +0000 VTuberバーチャル音楽TwitterYouTubeYouTuberバーチャルYouTuberホロライブホロライブプロダクションライブ兎田ぺこら有明有明アリーナ https://p2y.jp/?p=101823 <p> 2023年9月23日，Cover Co., Ltd.将举办该公司运营的VTuber经纪公司Hololive Productions旗下日本女团“Hololive”所属的Pekora Usada的首次个人现场表演。</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-1st-solo-live-usagi-the-megami-will-be-held-on-december-6-at-ariake-arena/">VTuber Pekora Usada 的第一次个人演唱会“Usagi the MEGAMI!!”将于 12 月 6 日在 Ariake Arena</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> 2023年9月23日（令和5年），Cover株式会社<strong>将举办</strong>该公司运营的VTuber经纪公司Hololive Productions旗下日本女团“Hololive”所属的<strong>Pekora</strong> Usada的首次个人现场公演已宣布<strong>“Usagi the MEGAMI!!”</strong>将于12月6日在有明竞技场举行。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="101826" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-1st-solo-live-usagi-the-megami-will-be-held-on-december-6-at-ariake-arena/vtuber_usada_pekora_1st_solo_live_usagi_the_megami_will_be_held_on_december_6_at_ariake_arena/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vtuber_usada_pekora_1st_solo_live_usagi_the_megami_will_be_held_on_december_6_at_ariake_arena.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_usada_pekora_1st_solo_live_usagi_th